7 mTLS
******

Install five files under ‘/etc/casmgr/mtls/’:

‘server.crt’, ‘server.key’
     Server certificate and private key (MCP/API listener).
‘ca.crt’
     Certificate authority for verifying peers.
‘client.crt’, ‘client.key’
     Client certificate for MCP proxy registration.

   Permissions (applied by ‘dpkg --configure casmgr-server’): directory
mode ‘0750’ ‘root:casgrp’; files mode ‘0640’.  Private keys must be
readable by ‘casuser’ via group ‘casgrp’.

   Paths in ‘config.json’ (see template for full structure):

"server": { "ssl": {
  "cert": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/server.crt",
  "key": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/server.key",
  "ca": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/ca.crt"
}},
"registration": { "ssl": {
  "cert": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/client.crt",
  "key": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/client.key",
  "ca": "/etc/casmgr/mtls/ca.crt"
}}


