13 Systemd
**********

‘casmgr.service’
     Single unit that runs the all-in-one container via ‘docker compose
     -f /etc/casmgr/docker-compose.yml up -d’ on start and ‘... down’ on
     stop.  Requires Docker.  Config and secrets are bind-mounted from
     ‘/etc/casmgr’ and ‘/var/casmgr’.

     sudo systemctl enable casmgr
     sudo systemctl start casmgr
     sudo systemctl status casmgr
     sudo systemctl restart casmgr
     sudo docker logs -f casmgr

   The package starts ‘casmgr’ automatically only when config has no
‘CHANGE_ME’ or ‘MCP_PROXY_HOST’ placeholders and all five mTLS files
exist.


